5000_08203af15d3a88a123b265168274f0d8.jpg&h=ffe2a030&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/10/185001_34c9fd0a38461ef470c5eb50bff0b25b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F185001_34c9fd0a38461ef470c5eb50bff0b25b.jpg&h=eace837a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/10/185003_113699ff85fea6b30f24c2d6ee787f07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F185003_113699ff85fea6b30f24c2d6ee787f07.jpg&h=3e4a58e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/10/185005_b6ee542f90d9c6ef61d460a42ec37208.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F185005_b6ee542f90d9c6ef61d460a42ec37208.jpg&h=5a2689cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/10/185006_bb1d52ee57ad1a8d92ce8bcc2cab3368.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F185006_bb1d52ee57ad1a8d92ce8bcc2cab3368.jpg&h=b34230b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男生購買自慰情趣用品「飛機杯」，通常不會大肆宣揚，但馬來西亞一名情趣用品女神Gatita Yan的顧客卻很不同，竟然樂於被公布出來，Gatita Yan會在《臉書》粉專po出顧客的照片「鼓勵」，「以後你不會再手酸了，飛機杯要好好用哦」、「包你射多多，每天爽爽睡覺」、「不要每天偷看我的照片打飛機了」。<br />\nGatita Yan身材姣好，經常在《臉書》粉專露出強大的事業線，更公開販售飛機杯，被稱為馬來西亞飛機杯女王，也吸引許多男性捧場購買，特別的是，通常買飛機杯打手槍似乎都是一件害羞的事，但Gatita Yan的顧客卻大方被女神公告長相。而且Gatita Yan的粉專有超過8萬人追蹤，這種讓幾萬人知道自己買飛機杯打手槍的感覺不知道如何啊！"},{"pid":"f6df0df945c2a58b21e0d56d8f05345210e28594","tid":525163,"uid":121393,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T10:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62233b2956c7a3da576701deebba13f5e90d8ab","tid":525163,"uid":121393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T10:54:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{